{"tid":2166328,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"20%受訪日企 考慮撤出中國","createTime":"2020-08-20T10:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:51:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a950b130060791fec1278b52ebadb4c13936e304","tid":2166328,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/INJBFYZIUZHLBNG6Z2A5UUQ6EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FINJBFYZIUZHLBNG6Z2A5UUQ6EU%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5aCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=6426ad5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FINJBFYZIUZHLBNG6Z2A5UUQ6EU%2F&h=b098dd03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/INJBFYZIUZHLBNG6Z2A5UUQ6EU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n20%受訪日企 考慮撤出中國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pz9zp8fWhwfcXoHKd8HNYmVRAJU=/1280x854/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWNUMKZBOFHLJFARGBAAOGYF6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPz9zp8fWhwfcXoHKd8HNYmVRAJU%3D%2F1280x854%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWNUMKZBOFHLJFARGBAAOGYF6I.jpg&h=423d3ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■受中美關係緊張影響，有日企考慮撒出中國。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國雖然是日本最大的貿易夥伴國，但受中美關係緊張影響，有日企考慮撒出中國。日經研究發佈一項調查指，46%受訪日企指美國對華制裁將有損其利潤；20%日企表示，正考慮將業務、運營基地及供應鏈撤出中國；絕大。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n日經研究於8月3至8月13日進行調查，採訪495間大中型非金融公司，收到約220家公司回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疫情加快業務遷移<br />\n<br />\n美國銀行（BofA）研究數據亦顯示，疫情加快國際公司將製造業務撤出中國，該些公司失去中國市場，未來五年或損失1萬億美元；不過該行表示長遠而言對企業有利。美銀全球研究部門主管Candace Browning表示，疫情導致全球80%的產業供應鏈中斷，逼使超過75%美歐製造業加快撤出中國。<br />\n<br />\n報告又顯示，疫情前企業供應鏈已從全球化變為在地化，主。。。。。。。。。"}]}